General Information

This oil brings certainty and relief to anxious states.

Also useful for: Nervous tension, stress and mild anxiety.

A powerful intense sweet earthy aroma with a slightly herbaceous undertone

Warnings

STORE BELOW 30C. NOT TO BE TAKEN ORALLY. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.

Ingredients

Pogostemon cablin leaf 1mL/mL

Directions

Adult: For the relief of NERVOUS TENSION, STRESS and MILD ANXIETY: add 6 drops to vaporiser or add 5 drops to 10mL Vegetable Glycerine or Full Cream Milk and add to bath water. If symptoms persist consult your health care practitioner.
